text: Zus & Zo is a 2001 Dutch romantic fantasy comedy movie directed by Paula van der Oest and starring Monic Hendrickx, Anneke Blok, Sylvia Poorta, Jacob Derwig, Halina Reijn, Annet Nieuwenhuyzen. It was nominated for an Academy Awards in 2003. ==Other websites== * Category:2001 romantic comedy movies Category:2001 fantasy movies Category:2001 LGBT movies Category:Dutch romance movies Category:Dutch comedy movies Category:Dutch LGBT movies Category:Movies directed by Paula van der Oest
